  <!-- 11. Description -->
  <dcterms:description>
    The Bamberger Symphoniker returns to Korea after two years, with Chief Conductor Jakub Hrůša and violin soloist Bomsori Kim.
    The program presents works representing Czech and German musical coexistence, from Wagner's early opera overture to Bruch's beloved violin concerto and Beethoven's festive Seventh Symphony.
  </dcterms:description>

